snippet.title: AMG DAO Gameplay Series - Ookeenga
snippet.description:
Ookeenga is a 3D gaming project which is built on the Binance Smart Chain. With breath-taking graphics, appealing world-building, and addictive gameplay, Ookeenga is ready to create an uniquely immersive play-own-earn experience.
INTENSE GAME MODES:
PvE: Build up your team, upgrade your Heroes and conquer infinite battles to take control of the Sacred Forest
PVP: Challenge the strongest in rank to earn rewards and bring the glorious victory for your forces

You can find more information about what are we doing and how you can find us:
https://linktr.ee/joinamg
